overview_of_class: This is a two hour weekly laboratory to be taken concurrently with Physics 130-2 or 135-2.  Enrollment in a lab is required when registered for a Physics 130 or 135 lecture.  Topics include electrostatics, magnetostatics, DC and AC circuits. On line pre-lab quizzes will be administered through CANVAS.
name: General Physics Laboratory
subject: PHYSICS
